$ VBA function: dateAdd

`dateAdd(…)` can be used to add *intervals* to a given point in time:

gh|about-VBA|/functions/dateAdd.vb||

The following expression evaluates to 2021-02-28:
code {
dateAdd("m", 1, #2021-01-31#)
code }

